P_HTM[1959]='*324. Bhikkhu atthatakathino phāsuvihāriko cīvaraṃ ādāya pakkamati – ‘‘amukaṃ nāma āvāsaṃ gamissāmi; tattha me phāsu bhavissati vasissāmi, no ce me phāsu bhavissati, amukaṃ nāma āvāsaṃ gamissāmi; tattha me phāsu bhavissati vasissāmi, no ce me phāsu bhavissati, amukaṃ nāma āvāsaṃ gamissāmi; tattha me phāsu bhavissati  vasissāmi, no ce me phāsu bhavissati, paccessa’’nti. Tassa bahisīmagatassa evaṃ hoti – ‘‘idhevimaṃ  cīvaraṃ kāressaṃ, na paccessa’’nti. So taṃ cīvaraṃ kāreti. Tassa bhikkhuno niṭṭhānantiko kathinuddhāro.*';
