P_HTM[2405]='*Tajjanīyakammakathā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[2406]='*243. Niyassakammakathā*';
P_HTM[2407]='*412. Idha  pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu bālo hoti abyatto āpattibahulo  anapadāno, gihisaṃsaṭṭho viharati ananulomikehi gihisaṃsaggehi. Tatra ce bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti – ‘‘ayaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu bālo abyatto āpattibahulo anapadāno, gihisaṃsaṭṭho viharati ananulomikehi gihisaṃsaggehi. Handassa mayaṃ niyassakammaṃ karomā’’ti. Te tassa niyassakammaṃ karonti – adhammena vaggā. So tamhā āvāsā aññaṃ āvāsaṃ gacchati. Tatthapi bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti – ‘‘ayaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu saṅghena niyassakammakato adhammena vaggehi. Handassa mayaṃ niyassakammaṃ karomā’’ti. Te tassa niyassakammaṃ karonti – adhammena samaggā…pe… dhammena vaggā… dhammapatirūpakena vaggā… dhammapatirūpakena samaggā…pe….*';
P_HTM[2408]='*Yathā heṭṭhā, tathā cakkaṃ kātabbaṃ.*';
P_HTM[2409]='*Niyassakammakathā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[2410]='*244. Pabbājanīyakammakathā*';
P_HTM[2411]='*413. Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kuladūsako hoti pāpasamācāro. Tatra ce bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti – ‘‘ayaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu kuladūsako pāpasamācāro. Handassa mayaṃ pabbājanīyakammaṃ karomā’’ti. Te tassa pabbājanīyakammaṃ karonti – adhammena vaggā. So tamhā āvāsā aññaṃ āvāsaṃ gacchati. Tatthapi bhikkhūnaṃ evaṃ hoti – ‘‘ayaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu saṅghena pabbājanīyakammakato adhammena vaggehi. Handassa mayaṃ pabbājanīyakammaṃ karomā’’ti. Te tassa pabbājanīyakammaṃ karonti – adhammena samaggā…pe… dhammena vaggā… dhammapatirūpakena vaggā… dhammapatirūpakena samaggā…pe….*';
